sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant ERC20 as ERC20 Token
    participant TE as TradingEngine
    participant PE as PriceEngine
    participant Math as MathLibrary
    participant TWAP as TWAPLibrary
    participant FM as FeeManager
    participant MV as MarketVault
    participant SM as SettlementManager
    participant PF as PulseFactory

    Note over U, PF: BUY FLOW (ACTIVE State)
    U->>TE: buy(viewId, side, amount)
    TE->>PF: getViewRecord(viewId)
    PF-->>TE: return (config)
    TE->>PE: quoteBuy(supplies, reserve, amount)
    PE->>Math: computeIndex(supplies)
    Math-->>PE: return index
    PE-->>TE: return (sharesOut, newIndex, newReserve)
    TE->>FM: recordFee(viewId, feeAmount)
    TE->>ERC20: safeTransferFrom(U, MV, netAmount)
    TE->>MV: deposit(netAmount)
    TE->>TWAP: tryRecordSnapshot(newIndex)
    TE-->>U: emit Bought, PulseIndexUpdated

    Note over U, PF: SELL FLOW (ACTIVE State)
    U->>TE: sell(viewId, side, shares)
    TE->>PE: quoteSell(supplies, reserve, shares)
    PE->>Math: computeIndex(supplies)
    Math-->>PE: return index
    PE-->>TE: return (amountOut, newIndex, newReserve)
    TE->>FM: recordFee(viewId, feeAmount)
    TE->>MV: withdraw(U, netAmountOut)
    TE->>TWAP: tryRecordSnapshot(newIndex)
    TE-->>U: emit Sold, PulseIndexUpdated

    Note over U, PF: LOCK FLOW (endTime reached)
    U->>TE: lockMarket(viewId)
    TE->>TWAP: finaliseTWAP()
    TWAP-->>TE: return finalTWAP
    TE->>TE: update status to LOCKED
    TE-->>U: emit MarketLocked, TWAPFinalised

    Note over U, PF: SETTLEMENT FLOW (LOCKED State)
    SM->>TE: getTWAP(viewId)
    TE-->>SM: return finalTWAP
    SM->>TE: setMarketStatus(SETTLEMENT)
    SM->>MV: settle(winners)
    SM->>TE: setMarketStatus(CLAIMABLE)
